==English==
===Adjective===
'''lexicographic'''

#Like a [[dictionary]], relating to [[lexicography]] (the writing of a dictionary).



===Usage note===
*The phrase '''lexicographic order''' means in '''alphabetical order'''.  It is a common term in computer science.  It may indicate that numbers are to be treated as [[string]]s so ''10'' comes before ''2'' because there is no positional weighting and the symbol ''1'' comes before ''2''.

